{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>name</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><em><code>message</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>BroadcastChannel.onmessage</code></strong> イベントハンドラは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> 型の <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> イベントがこの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a> によって受信されたときに実行する関数を指定するプロパティです。</span> このようなイベントは、チャネルに放送されるメッセージとともにブラウザーによって送信されます。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>注:</strong> この機能は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 内で利用可能です</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>channel</em>.onmessage = <em>function</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"values","title":"Values","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>function</code> は、接尾辞 <code>()</code> もパラメーターも含まないユーザー定義関数の名前や、 <code>function(event) {...}</code> などの無名関数宣言です。 イベントハンドラには、イベントを含む単一のパラメータが常に1つあります。 ここでは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> 型です。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>bc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onmessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ev</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message event received!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/comms.html#handler-broadcastchannel-onmessage\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">BroadcastChannel.onmessage の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.onmessage","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>ブラウザコンテキスト間でやり取りするもう1つの、よりヘビー級の方法: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage イベントハンドラは、MessageEvent 型の message イベントがこの BroadcastChannel によって受信されたときに実行する関数を指定するプロパティです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/conflicting/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/conflicting/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage | MDN","noIndexing":true}}